{"tid":528902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全球暖化撚正on99","createTime":"2018-01-14T10:53:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T04:59:06.000Z","uid":149978,"like":3,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fa9909138a4aeac3aded6747c13b8b4916ddc020","tid":528902,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T10:53:09.000Z","msg":"環保就係好事，環保旨在改善空氣和水質。但講到污染會搞到世界末日，就係on撚99的環保膠和環保撚，宣傳的杞人憂天想法。<br />\n<br />\n環保撚中，暖化撚係最on9。唔係話冇全球暖化，根本地球多數地方都偏冷。香港亞熱帶冬天都咁凍。新加坡呢些熱帶地方的人生活質素卻不錯。根本地球暖一些，世界更美好。<br />\n<br />\n好啦，如果冰川溶化，海平面上升左又如何？一個城市100年已經發展得成熟。而且樓齡100年都要拆啦。海平面真係上升左，都有晒時間比居民和政府搬遷。<br />\n<br />\n咁少問題吹到咁大，居心何在？"},{"pid":"fc8def8dfecc9e4466b18c862c4394cc7bfc92f1","tid":528902,"uid":4525,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T10:55:25.000Z","msg":"唔吹大D撚有人理咩"},{"pid":"80bd1b8945babe9dda801012ea7d6a0ab34fec41","tid":528902,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T10:55:57.000Z","msg":"暖化撚的膠文共賞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/528844/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/528844/page/2</a>"},{"pid":"a0c5020e3684fd7ebc485474c53ee6cf3f018e20","tid":528902,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc8def8dfecc9e4466b18c862c4394cc7bfc92f1","tid":528902,"uid":4525,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T10:55:25.000Z","msg":"唔吹大D撚有人理咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T10:57:25.000Z","msg":"物極必反。<br />\n吹咁大，最終令人覺得環保人士係環保膠，環保撚。"},{"pid":"ba618575340c98078eba4dd3f32ad87b84eef85c","tid":528902,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T11:02:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>暖化撚的膠文共賞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/528844/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/528844/page/1</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n修正"},{"pid":"21f3039b0d7f04b5280c32673c69822f5cb59121","tid":528902,"uid":45977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-